      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/22/2/10/55",
      "text": [
        ": للقائم غيبتان، يشهد في إحديهما المواسمَ يرى الناس ولا يرونه فيه."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.abdullah-al-shahin": [
          "(16) Muhammad bin Ya’qoob al-Kulayni narrated from al-Husayn bin Muhammad from Ja’far bin Muhammad from al-Qassim bin Issma’eel from Yahya bin al-Muthanna from Abdullah bin Bukayr from Obayd bin Zurara that Abu Abdullah as-Sadiq (as) had said: “Al-Qa’im (as) disappears twice. During one of his disappearances, he attends the seasons of hajj. He sees the people but they do not see him.”"
        ]
      }
    },
